---
title: Curried Chicken Salad Wraps with Golden Raisins & Cabbage-Carrot Slaw
description: A mix of sour cream, mayo, and curry spices coat chicken and golden raisins in creamy, golden-hued flavor. Then this aromatic chicken salad is stuffed inside soft tortillas along with cabbage and carrots for even more crunch and color. Glorious texture, rich flavors, brilliant hues—yep, that’s a wrap!
